    "As shown in Table 1, CHAMELEON consistently outperforms all baselines.",
    "Remarkably, these improvements are achieved with minimal user history data and without any training and fine-tuning, surpassing an SFT-based method (ALOE).",
    "These results validate our claim that CHAMELEON can effectively align LLMs to individual user preferences.",
    "We also assess CHAMELEON's ability to personalize for new, unseen users who have no prior history.",
    "In this evaluation, we run both CHAMELEON and ALOE on the LaMP training split and evaluate their performance on test sam-ples from users not included in the training data."
